	measure '% Orders Late 3+ Days' = ```
			
			VAR Late3 =
			    CALCULATE (
			        DISTINCTCOUNT ( FACT_FULFILMENT[order_id] ),
			        FACT_FULFILMENT[is_late_by_days] >= 3
			    )
			RETURN
			DIVIDE ( Late3, [Fulfilment Orders] )
			
			```
		formatString: 0.00%;-0.00%;0.00%
		displayFolder: F. Op Severity
		lineageTag: 0022edc2-b2f5-4144-843d-fa06e8451401

