	measure 'Cohort Retained Customers (Selected Period)' = ```
			
			VAR ActivityMinYM =
			    VALUE ( MIN ( DIM_DATE[YearMonthSort] ) )
			RETURN
			CALCULATE (
			    DISTINCTCOUNT ( FACT_SALES[customer_id] ),
			    FILTER (
			        ALL ( DIM_CUSTOMER ),
			        DIM_CUSTOMER[First Purchase YearMonthSort] < ActivityMinYM
			    )
			)
			
			```
		formatString: 0
		displayFolder: H. Customer Logic
		lineageTag: a0d8cb81-4f29-4795-abd0-bc744483cbf6

	measure 'Cohort Retention % (Post-Acquisition)' = ```
			
